=99s Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga earned the distinction of being the summer=E2=
=80=99s most high-profile tentpole flop ($172 million worldwide). Twisters =
overperformed domestically ($239.6 million and counting), courtesy of Unive=
rsal, but Warners failed to translate that globally ($95.1 million). Unfort=
unately for Uni, the two studios share in the total pot equally.

