           <p style=3D"margin: 0; color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Welcome back to a jam-packed i=
ssue of What I=E2=80=99m Hearing+, Tuesday=E2=80=99s extra scoop of creamy =
entertainment industry intelligence. Today we=E2=80=99ve got a tag-team: <b=
>Eriq Gardner</b> has a few newsy updates, including a pretty shocking new =
front in CAA=E2=80=99s war against its hated defectors at Range Media. Then=
 our box office expert <b>Scott Mendelson</b> is here with his 7 important =
takeaways from the surprisingly not-terrible summer at the movies.      <br=
/><br/><i>Okay, let=E2=80=99s start with Eriq=E2=80=A6</i><br/><br/></p>
