 legal action. I=E2=80=99ve heard it=E2=80=99s under consideration. Stay tu=
ned.<br/><br/></li><li><i>Is Sunday Ticket still in legal jeopardy?</i>: An=
 appeal was practically guaranteed after federal judge <b>Philip Gutierrez<=
/b> reversed a jury=E2=80=99s $4.7 billion verdict against the NFL and its =
